- [[Add Custom CSS to Org Reveal]]

- add the following contents into your custom css

  ``` css
  .reveal h1,
  .reveal h2,
  .reveal h3,
  .reveal h4,
  .reveal h5,
  .reveal h6 {
      text-transform: none !important;
  }
  ```
